songs.title: Who Knows, Who Cares
songs.album: Battle of the Bands Contest in Torquay
songs.lyrics:
[Verse]

Who knows, who cares what you are
Who knows, who cares you're no star
No one wants to be with you
No one's gonna listen

[Verse]

Who knows, who cares what you are
Who knows, who cares you're no star
No one wants to be with you
No one's gonna listen

[Bridge]

[Chorus]

Cut yourself but nobody knows it
Call for help but no one knows it

[Verse]

Who knows, who cares what you are
Who knows, who cares you're no star
No one wants to be with you
No one's gonna listen too

[Bridge]

[Chorus]

Cut yourself but nobody knows it
Call for help but no one knows it

[Chorus]

Cut yourself but nobody knows it
Call for help but no one knows it

[Outro]
